        <mxCell id="bp1_desc" value="&lt;span&gt;Provide Examples in Prompt&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;• Include 1-2 examples of good/bad outputs&lt;br&gt;• Show expected score for each example&lt;br&gt;• More examples ≠ better (1-shot often optimal)&lt;br&gt;• Keep examples relevant to task" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=#f3e5f5;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=1;fontSize=11;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=#4a148c;spacingLeft=8;fontStyle=0;spacingTop=4;" parent="1" vertex="1">
